American Electric Power

The seven operating companies of American Electric Power (AEP) have
adopted the AEP name. The seven -- Appalachian Power, Columbus
Southern Power, Ohio Power, Indiana Michigan Power, Kentucky Power,
Wheeling Power, and Kingsport Power -- all will be known as AEP.



