Star/Texaco says deals aren't final, but Global Petroleum
confirms it will buy White Fuels (Boston).  Petroleum Heat &
Power confirms it will buy Texaco Home Heat (Long Island).
Santoro Oil has yet to confirm buying Kelleher Oil (Providence,
R.I.).  Peterson Oil (Worcester, Mass.) has yet to confirm
buying Coughlin-Donaghue.



