VIDEO WEEK via NewsNet
January 1, 1996

     Trident Entertainment has entered video arena with

     Trident Entertainment has entered video arena with
instructional All Pro Sports Football Series featuring NFL players. 
Series will be available at midyear;  company is in discussions
with potential distributors, said Bruce Singman, vp-business &
legal affairs, CEO of All Pro Sports Video Productions and lawyer
who has represented NFL players.  Series will consist of 12
football titles featuring Jerry Rice, Reggie White, Ronnie Lott,
others.  Topics will include physical conditioning, game
strategies, insider tips, all offensive and defensive positions,
coaching video.  Tapes will include computer graphics, upbeat
music, NFL highlights.



