titles are Going to School, Learning Is Everywhere, Our Earth: 
Clean and Green, The Doctor Your Friend.  Consumers will be offered
2 puppets -- X the Owl and Daniel the Striped Tiger -- for price of
one, $12.95.  Titles will be advertised in Video Business, Discount
Store News, Parents' Magazine, Sesame Street Parents' Magazine.



