     Tower Records has expanded into Canada, opening 22,500-sq.-ft.

     Tower Records has expanded into Canada, opening 22,500-sq.-ft.
store in Toronto.  Outlet is stocked with 100,000 music CDs, 10,000
videos, laserdiscs and CD-ROM titles, 14,000 books.  It has 50
listening stations.  Tower operates 150 stores in 12 countries.



